{"tid":1325517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族明發起靜默遊行 衝突陸續有來","createTime":"2019-07-17T01:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T01:55:44.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3c8b42653d7a0aaad747d999034bc26fd2b2ac","tid":1325517,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8A%80%E9%AB%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%98%8E%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%9D%9C%E9%BB%98%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BE%86-214500983.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%258A%2580%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%25BB%2598%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BE%2586-214500983.html&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSQ3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=a035e38b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8A%80%E9%AB%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%98%8E%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E9%9D%9C%E9%BB%98%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%99%B8%E7%BA%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BE%86-214500983.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7ogn1b8VDx1EjHlOgyDefg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/043eefa12df2f7d234a76253013f2fa4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7ogn1b8VDx1EjHlOgyDefg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F043eefa12df2f7d234a76253013f2fa4&h=5704066e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有退休人士於明日發起「銀髮族靜默遊行」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】修訂《逃犯條例》引發的遊行示威陸續有來！有退休人士於明日（17日）發起「銀髮族靜默遊行」，由中環遮打花園遊行至政府總部，要求政府撤回修例、撤銷對已被捕人士的檢控、立即停止搜捕、成立獨立調查委員會徹查警民衝突及重啟政改實行雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n冀釐清律政司司長鄭若驊之責任<br />\n<br />\n就遊行申請不反對通知書的楊女士表示，即使現時政府指撤回修例亦無助解決問題，但政府亦應撤回。她指，政府必須成立獨立調查委員會，澄清政府、律政司司長鄭若驊在整件事的責任，而年輕人在反修例的示威中付出沉重代價，認為應要把握時機支持年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n料尚有八次遊行示威 東西夾擊<br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學前副教授何芝君表示，警民衝突已有升級迹象，認為警方在權力不對等的情況下，不要主動挑釁示威者的情緒，甚至封鎖所有疏散路線，引起公眾恐慌。她表示，前線警察聽令而行，認為示威有衝突和流血，警察也是代罪羔羊和受害者，對此感到同情，認為作出暴力清場決定的警隊高層需負上責任。<br />\n<br />\n自政府提出修例以來，已引發多次遊行示威衝突，根據網上流傳的訊息，明日至八月上旬，至少尚有八次遊行示威活動，特別在本月廿八日，更分別舉行將軍澳遊行及港島西遊行，實行「東西夾擊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7X8D5y87ZwBOu4y55QBrfw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/b98f9581ed064009a7377910efc175e3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7X8D5y87ZwBOu4y55QBrfw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fb98f9581ed064009a7377910efc175e3&h=0e91f7a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各區遊行示威陸續有來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}